TextData[
{"The temporal scale ",Cell[
BoxData[FormBox[TemplateBox[Association["boxes" -> FormBox[
SubscriptBox[StyleBox["t","TI"],StyleBox["o","TI"]],TraditionalForm],"errors" -> {},
"input" -> "$t_o$","state" -> "Boxes"],"TeXAssistantTemplate"],TraditionalForm]],
ExpressionUUID -> "5afe2963-7155-7d41-a09a-d2fc5b34a94f"]," is then determined by minimizing the covariance-weighted ",Cell[
